    "body": "ugh @its-19818942118 was right... it was my zshrc all along. these two lines to be more specific:\r\n```sh\r\nautoload -Uz compinit && compinit\r\ncompinit -d \"$XDG_CACHE_HOME\"/zsh/zcompdump-\"$ZSH_VERSION\"\r\n```\r\n",
